social_posts.post_text: Back to my roots 💁🏻‍♀️. Thank you @kristinaruddick 📸 and @kristinwaynemakeup 💄for making me feel like the best version of myself❤️✨
New Year, New Look, New Baby 👶🏼🥰🙊 Coming Spring ‘23!!! #hunintheoven

When @cameronpicstv asked if I’d be interested in coming out to play @jonathanmalen’s girlfriend on the new season of #PrettyHardCases, I knew it would be one of my greatest acting challenges to date 😂 Meet Yolanda “Yoyo” Pesci 💅 Special shout out to @lifeofmanek & @kimprimeau for bringing this unbelievable lewk to life. And of course to the hilarious @meredithmacneill & @acmoore9!! Catch it tonight on @cbc and @cbcgem at 9pm!! 💅
She’s back and she’s serving shoulder pads! Tonight at 9pm on @cbc & @cbcgem #prettyhardcases
Happy 3rd birthday to my garbage loving, interpretive dancing, one of a kind, funny little Charlie. We love you so much 💙🚛🌈

Leo Wilder Malen 🦁🧡🦁 

On 4.27.23 this guy shot out of the birth canal like a cannonball less than an hour after arriving at the hospital. I asked Jonathan if (after I came out of newborn fog) I would regret posting this photo from RIGHT after giving birth. He said no, it was real. And you know what? It doesn’t get more real than child birth without drugs after a tough pregnancy!!!!Tell me what is more powerful than the female body, I dare you!!! We love you so much sweet Leo 🦁🧡🦁
A Bris, a BBQ and all our Guncles . A month and a day with Leo 🧡

I am so excited to be partnering once again with @nuna_canada. I’ll be sharing some of my favourite products from this 🇨🇦 brand that I ACTUALLY use in my day to day life and my kids love! We all know and trust their car seats but have you tried the LEAF grow swing? If your baby loves to be rocked and held constantly (🙋🏼‍♀️🤪) the LEAF will be a game changer. The ultra smooth and quiet (!!) motion calms Leo right down. My back thanks you, Nuna. And the best part? It evolves with him into a toddler chair so we can use it for years to come. Doesn’t hurt that it looks chic too. Style and substance, we love to see it! #nunababy #nunacanada #nunaleafgrow #nunamom #ad

A very delayed but necessary post! The same week I brought my new baby into the world, @zoelisterjones brought hers too! I have finally had the chance to binge #SLIPtheSeries and I still can’t believe I got to be part of this show!!! Zoe, I have always admired you but watching how you work and lead a set with grace and positivity was the biggest inspiration to me 😭. Thank you you for the gift of 🌹. Slip is now available to stream on your Roku device or at www.therokuchannel.com! This will be your new favourite show- truuuust me!!
Thank you for the bday love all week!!!! Finally saw Barbie & hung out with these hunks. Soaking up the last of summer & excited for the year ahead. Have a beautiful long weekend my hunnies 💫💕✨💕💫💕✨

Such a cool night at the @tiff_net Tribute Awards honouring inspiring folks like @patriciaarquette @officialspikelee & @slevydirect (who directed the In A Heartbeat pilot maybe 25 years ago!!) But the most special part? Being back in the room where it all began for us. We shot Take The Lead in this very room almost 20 years ago. I think there’s a “how it started/how it’s going” post here somewhere. 🤩🥰🤩
Perhaps not the biggest news on @deadline today (#sagaftrastrong!!!) but still noteworthy! Dream team, dream material, feeling very thankful and excited for this one!!!

2023 was filled with a lot of happy faces, some truly life changing experiences and challenges… and pumping. So much pumping. Wishing you all a healthy and happy New Year. Excited for what’s next ✨✨✨
🎤BYE!🎤
